data.description: Welcome Home! This great colonial offers just what you need! Step inside to a large dining room and cozy living room great for entertaining. The kitchen includes a center island beautiful tiled in Ceramic! Bedrooms and closets are generously sized offering lots of storage space. Master bedroom provides a large walk in closet! come and take a look!
